Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.09,0:00:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先向大家说声 谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好突然哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在看水星领航员的各位观众
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了各位给我们带来的暖风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级感谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是美好的奇迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微妙的让人害羞的台词 禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 持续到昨天的雨终于停歇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是个非常好的天气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.87,0:00:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说如此 但因为艾莉西亚前辈有事要出去一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就临时歇业了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 蓝华有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝要上学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此这般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和亚利亚社长也决定出门去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:36.28,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 小小的秘密之地…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近全是住宅区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此在做导游的时候不会到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也是新威尼斯的另一副面容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论何时来都是不变的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨一直下到昨天才停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里一定很值得期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了哦 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然有好多好多衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 这里有更多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晾着的衣服舒舒服服地在空中畅游呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么就把衣服弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那里有水坑…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才刚洗完衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空中邮递员哥哥还夸我很活泼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那是活泼过头了啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里也能看到钟楼呢 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我来到这个城市 就没有改变过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子有点饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们去吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如我们去吃那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次在附近的店里吃到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个让人兴奋紧张的料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 是二人份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待期待 期待期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 很好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从小时候起就喜欢把这家店的粗粮饼堆得像火山一样吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好有历史感哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次来的时候我们试试那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是弹面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待期待 期待期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待期待 期待期待 期待期待 期待期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:07:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好玩～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好吃呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子好饱哦 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 肚子饿了 去吃披萨…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是鬓子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的休息日 我还想跟艾莉西亚小姐偶遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不识相的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 还是揪揪她的鬓发当作打招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那边看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里在哪里在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟丢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大妈 给我一个番茄披萨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长 新的洋装到货了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿晓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的中学同窗会阿晓你去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就把我们两个的回执寄出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个披萨好像很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 谢谢的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我的披萨 在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很合适哦 太好了呢 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佛洛林咖啡馆的装修开始了哦 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会变得闪闪发亮的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敏捷的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是神出鬼没的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 门打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般游客不能从这边进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去搭电梯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用不用 下次再来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 跟艾莉西亚小姐问好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼哼哼 这次你跑不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 马尾男？他在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级偷偷摸摸的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这是去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跟过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没来这里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是观光胜地 所以附近人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不可思议的是 谁都不会注意到这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华和爱丽丝 说不定连艾莉西亚前辈都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只属于我的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样坐着的话 就没有人会发现我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新威尼斯的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也在一点一点地变化着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪都找不到上去的楼梯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到底是怎么上去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…是那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没上锁 没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个寺院一目了然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马…屁屁…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级双料鬓发征服！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道厉害了吧 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷袭太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于让我抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 为什么本大爷要尾行鬓子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这绝不是在尾行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来 你居然能找到这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边上楼的楼梯很不起眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人都不会注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 对本大爷来说是易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你到这种地方来干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实这里有一位让我十分在意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我偶尔会偷偷来见他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幽会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不过亚利亚社长也一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直孤单一人 从这里眺望着大海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬓子啊 你说的他到底是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你他是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说那个了 晓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把头放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能跟这位用一样的视线眺望这里的景色了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这不变的风景之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍会有许多高兴的事情 崭新的事情 悲伤的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些事情堆积起了每个日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后慢慢改变着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像云的形状和海的颜色在变换一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静地…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位先生 在不为人知的漫长数百年间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直守护着这个广场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然非常美好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却也有点悲伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我啊 把这里当成了我的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}恭喜你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会告诉别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是我们的秘密基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本大爷和鬓子的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有亚利亚社长和那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 无视掉我们 你们继续 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰二位了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.57,0:22:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是超级路人甲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥斯拉 不准误会！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.64,0:22:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}不要告诉艾莉西亚小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.70,0:22:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我的秘密基地啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.96,0:22:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.77,0:22:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始 这里变成了大家的秘密基地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城市在长久的不变中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉地在改变着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己一定也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.97,0:22:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见面的时候 新威尼斯和灯里姐姐会有些许的变化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 莫非我也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.17,0:23:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.22,0:23:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.32,0:24:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…超级大谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.49,0:24:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小后辈 你眼神好认真
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.33,0:24:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么谜团啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「哎呀哎呀 呵呵」的谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.70,0:24:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.52,0:24:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那次 精彩的课外教学…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.14,0:24:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:59.07,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}憶えていますか？ あの日を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:09.02,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ふと感じた ときめきを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:19.11,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:23.47,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:30.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}見とれてると 目が合って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:35.01,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}笑顔こぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}まるで スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:49.06,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\an7}いつまでも 手を振りたい日々
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:53.35,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ここに たしかに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:58.88,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君といた証
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.63,0:02:03.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ずっと スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:13.02,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}この先も 続いてる道がある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:21.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}次の坂を 登ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:26.51,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)}また会いましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:59.07,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}可曾记得？ 那一天
